properties.title: Mt. Baker
properties.description: @gletham GIS, Social, Mobile Tech Images posted a photo: Looking East from Vancouver Island towards Washington State and Mt. Baker. Note, from Victoria BC, the view of Mt Baker can be dramatically different depending on where you are situated in Victoria. Drive a mile or two or go to a slight elevation change and the mountain appears very different. For photos, in late afternoon when the sun is low and in the West Baker lights up and looks quite amazing.
